OL,3,CPolice drop manslaughter probe into
OL,4,Cexplosion that killed four people
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police say there
OL,7,Fisn't enough evidence to charge anyone
OL,8,Fwith manslaughter after three men and
OL,9,Fa teenager died in an explosion at
OL,10,FAvonmouth.
OL,12,FLuke Wheaton, 16, from Bradley Stoke,
OL,13,FRay White, 57, from Portishead, Brian
OL,14,FVickery, 63, from Clevedon, and Mike
OL,15,FJames, 64, from Bath, died in the
OL,16,Fincident at the Wessex Water site on
OL,17,FDecember 3 2020
OL,19,FThe blast happened in a silo at a
OL,20,Fwater recycling centre that held
OL,21,Ftreated biosolids.
