OL,3,CPolice drop manslaughter probe into
OL,4,Cexplosion that killed four people
OL,6,FMr James was a contractor working at
OL,7,Fthe site, while Mr Vickery and Mr
OL,8,FWhite were employees of Wessex Water
OL,9,Fand Luke was an apprentice at the firm.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police said its
OL,12,Fmajor crime investigation team had
OL,13,Fbeen leading the inquiry into the
OL,14,Fcause of the explosion, assisted by
OL,15,Fthe Health and Safety Executive.
OL,17,FA force spokesman said the
OL,18,Finvestigation had focused on whether
OL,19,Fany individuals were responsible, as
OL,20,Fwell as whether any health and safety
OL,21,Foffences had been committed.
