OL,3,CPolice drop manslaughter probe into
OL,4,Cexplosion that killed four people
OL,6,FDetectives, along with HSE
OL,7,Finvestigators, recently met with the
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service to review
OL,9,Fthe case and it was decided there was
OL,10,F"insufficient evidence to provide a
OL,11,Frealistic prospect of a criminal
OL,12,Fconviction for manslaughter".
OL,14,FThe HSE will now work to establish
OL,15,Fwhether criminal offences may have
OL,16,Fbeen committed under the Health and
OL,17,FSafety at Work etc Act 1974.
