OL,3,CPolice drop manslaughter probe into
OL,4,Cexplosion that killed four people
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Almond,
OL,7,Fof Avon and Somerset Police, said:
OL,8,F"Throughout our inquiry the families
OL,9,Fof Luke, Ray, Brian and Mike have been
OL,10,Ffirmly in our thoughts.
OL,12,F"The families have demonstrated great
OL,13,Fdignity and patience while we carried
OL,14,Fout our inquiries and I'd like to
OL,15,Fpublicly thank them for their support
OL,16,Fand understanding over the past three
OL,17,Fand a half years.
