OL,6,F"Inquiries of this kind are extremely
OL,7,Fcomplex and require the support of
OL,8,Fother agencies to gather evidence and
OL,9,Fthen a variety of experts to help us
OL,10,Finterpret what that evidence tells us.
OL,12,F"In this case, the evidence we've
OL,13,Fgathered doesn't reach the extremely
OL,14,Fhigh threshold to prosecute any
OL,15,Fcriminal offence of manslaughter."
OL,17,FIn tributes released through the
OL,18,Fpolice following the tragedy, Luke was
OL,19,Fdescribed as "the most gorgeous,
OL,20,Floving, happy, talented, perfect son".
