OL,6,FMr White's family said he was "a
OL,7,Fwonderful son, brother and father to
OL,8,Fhis two sons", while Mr Vickery's
OL,9,Ffamily paid tribute to his "cheeky and
OL,10,Fwicked sense of humour".
OL,12,FMr James's family described him as a
OL,13,F"brother, husband, father and grampy",
OL,14,Fadding that he would be missed.
