OL,6,FA Wessex Water spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We're continuing to work with the
OL,8,FHealth and Safety Executive as they
OL,9,Fcarry out their investigations and are
OL,10,Fcommitted to understanding why the
OL,11,Fincident happened. The four colleagues
OL,12,Fwill always be in the thoughts of
OL,13,Feveryone connected to Wessex Water."
